Quick navigation of bookmarks from your new tab page. 

Features
Minimal aesthetic, clutter free
Pinned folder for immediate access.
Intuitively navigate your bookmarks using the mouse wheel to return up folders.
Assign a color to any folder.
Open all bookmarks in folder option.
Find/Filter bookmarks.
Add/Edit/Move and reorder of bookmarks directly from new tab.
